item.title: Trap Remixes
item.dc:creator: @tyb97 tyb97
item.description:
@tyb97 wrote:

Soulcist:

Listened for a few minutes and thought it wasn’t that bad, don’t think I could stand the entire thing or more than 30 minutes of it but it’s not bad. I’m sure if I listened long enough that I would find something I like or can deal with a lot more. I recently found a rapper that I have fallen in love with and I usually HATE a lot of Rap music, especially the mainstream BS.

If you find a trap remix of a song you like it’s alot different.
